##Usings

#Global

to add a global using (affects all files in project), add this line to any file at project root
<code>
global using System.Linq;
</code>
Replace "System.Linq" with any library

OR

add this line to the *.csproj file
<code>
	<itemGroup>
		<using Include="System.Linq" />
	</itemGroup>
</code>
this can be mixed with other tag types within one itemGroup
I recommend this option so all the global usings are in one consistent place